{"tid":1040153,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"許晉亨生日唔理老婆　李嘉欣呷醋嗌出大招","createTime":"2019-02-28T01:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T03:41:48.000Z","uid":48905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"84255c351bb465e46b6a3ec081623a6a9d4077e6","tid":1040153,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:25:20.000Z","msg":"前港姐李嘉欣同老公許晉亨向來恩愛，今日係許晉亨嘅57歲生日，但嘉欣喺網上大爆老公竟對另一位「女性」更溫柔！不過原來嘉欣所指只係愛貓，見佢甫出老公同愛貓嘅合照，仲一副好溫柔嘅樣，難怪嘉欣假裝「投訴」話：「在老公生日的今天，我忽然感到他對另一位女性更柔軟 於是我决定 ....今晩要出大招 ... 等着瞧吧！」網民都話呢個另類放閃，一樣閃爆！ <br />\n<br />\n去到晚上，李嘉欣喺微博上載同許晉亨慶生嘅相，佢留言：「愛心港式黑森林蛋糕 ！ Happy birthday love！我真係恭喜你呀！」相信個蛋糕真係甜到漏喇！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cfeNKwb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcfeNKwb.png&h=2210cfcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">李嘉欣個黑森林好正咁。</span>"},{"pid":"16eeef5094b09cbfc64b665be757265fd9038cbf","tid":1040153,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:27:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5274bd92f903ae2ff98c9f70dfb6f51ef9ce321e","tid":1040153,"uid":118758,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:35:21.000Z","msg":"李嘉欣個黑森林好正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d82851ef884fba38b4571484bcffc3b0fc4b40","tid":1040153,"uid":17545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  比比都唔登我既大招：高潮腳個張相<br />\n咁你出post 嚟把撚啊？"},{"pid":"c641697b7c59301a8567f60a5b26f70b80e5985d","tid":1040153,"uid":48905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d2d82851ef884fba38b4571484bcffc3b0fc4b40","tid":1040153,"uid":17545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead